hod of Moments, accounts for\nthe moments of the joint PDF of progress variable and enthalpy coupled to a\nQuenching-Flamelet Generated Manifold. In the a priori analysis both turbulence\nchemistry interaction PDF closure models show a high accuracy in the core flow.\nIn the near-wall region, however, only the Conditional Quadrature Method of\nMoments approach is suitable to predict the flame structures.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 7 Dec 2022 17:11:26 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-12-08"}
