ate the catalog, its reported\nuncertainties, and biases using synthetic injection tests. We believe MADGICS\nprovides a viable path forward for large-scale spectral line measurements in\nthe presence of complex spectral contamination.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 7 Dec 2022 19:00:00 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 20 Jan 2023 00:34:18 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-01-23"}
